Hi,

brian d foy wrote:
> At the moment the file test operators that I expect to return true or
> false do, but the true is the filename.

that helps chaining of file test:

$fn ~~ :t ~~ :x
or something.
If you want a boolean, use
? $fn ~~ :x
or something.

